    Title: Bhagavad-Gitâ
    Location: VII 14
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=Mâyâ and Magic
Glossary:
  - Term: gunas
    Definition: |
      The three tendencies in Prakriti (the substantial pole of existence)
      pervading all manifestation： Sattva. ascending, luminous; Rajas.
      expansive, fiery; Tamas. descending, obscure.
---
Verily this divine Mâyâ of mine, composed of Gunas, is difficult to surmount;
those who take refuge in Me alone, they cross over this Mâyâ.
